      <div class="layout__item layout__item--body">
        <h2><b>Adam Buksh</b></h2>

        <p>
          Adam is a Glasgow based actor who works in a wide variety of styles.
          He has performed in modern adaptations of "Julius Caesar" (Regal
          Bathgate) and "Macbeth" (Proteus Theatre Company), new writing
          "Burning Bright" and "The Great Replacement" in this year's A Play, a
          Pie and a Pint Spring Season. He's very excited to be working with
          Matchmaker Theatre Production's "The Real William Shakespeare". Enjoy
          the show and remember "We are such stuff as dreams are made on and our
          little life is rounded with a sleep".
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="layout">
      <div class="layout__item layout__item--figure">
